Project details

Whether you need a stunning design from scratch, expert customization of existing themes, or help setting up payments, apps, and marketing I'm your one-stop Shopify shop. Forget template blues, let's build a store that reflects your vision and drives your business.

What will you get if you hire me as Shopify Expert:

Shopify Expert:
Free theme or Premium theme or Dawn Theme Install + 1 Home Page + 5 product uploads + google analytics

Shopify Pro:
Design according to your details + convert into Shopify Theme 2.0 + 7 pages include contact form + 20 product upload + google analytics + Meta Tags SEO + Shopify Speed optimization

Shopify Master:
Design according to your details + convert into Shopify Theme 2.0 + 10 pages include contact form + 50 product upload + google analytics + Meta Tags SEO + Speed optimization

Shopify Theme Store is an eCommerce business model and is considered a medium-risk business. Most of the money in this business model is spent on advertisements because drop shippers rely on paid marketing efforts to sell their products.

Im Siddiq Sethi! Im a Shopify Developer, WordPress Developer, and e-commerce expert with over 7 years of experience. Whether you need a fully customized Shopify store, a responsive WordPress website, or a complete WooCommerce solution, Im here to make it happen. My goal is to turn your online presence into a high-performing, revenue-generating website.
